text: The Iron Heel () is a 1919 Russian silent movie directed by Vladimir Gardin, Andrey Gorchilin, Olga Preobrazhenskaya, Yevgeny Ivanov-Barkov, Leonid Leonidov and Tamara Glebova.ЖЕЛЕЗНАЯ ПЯТАЖЕЛЕЗНАЯ ПЯТА (1919) It stars Olga Bonus, Anatoli Gorchilin, and Aleksandra Khokhlova. == References == ==Other websites== * Category:1919 movies Category:Russian silent movies Category:Movies directed by Vladimir Gardin Category:Movies directed by Olga Preobrazhenskaya
